Since this is the same problem as your previous thread, please keep the discussion there.

Limelight not appearing in Frc Driver station Dashboard Electrical
after opening SmartDashboard you must add a CameraServer stream to see the video feed from the limelight. You can do this by clicking on “View” on the top-right, then “Add…” then “CameraServer Stream Viewer”, you should see a video feed of your limelight on SmartDashboard now. If you can’t see the video feed from the limelight, then right click on the box that appears and edit it so that it displays a video feed from the limelight.
